text: The magic has finally arrived, so get the family together for a holiday spectacular from the most magical place on Earth. Enjoy The Wonderful World of Disney: Magical Holiday Celebration, tonight at 8|7c on ABC.
Happy Thanksgiving from our family to yours!
The Magical Holiday Celebration calls for Turkey Time!
Who's ready for some Disney magic? @Matt_Morrison and @EmmaBunton join @JessePalmerTV as hosts for The Wonderful World of Disney: Magical Holiday Celebration, tomorrow at 8|7c on ABC.
Get a jumpstart on your holiday shopping with up to 30% off at the ABC Shop. https://shopabctv.com/store/?utm_source=ABCSocial&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=BF_Twitter_2019
Nashville is a wild place! Don't miss Brad Paisley Thinks He's Special Tuesday at 8|7c on ABC. #BradPaisleySpecial

We've got another thing to be thankful for: Get an exclusive behind-the-scenes looks at Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker and Star Wars: Rise of the Resistance tomorrow during the Wonderful World of Disney: Magical Holiday Celebration!
Snoopy's got a big feast prepared for A Charlie Brown Thanksgiving, tonight at 8|7c on ABC!

Don't miss the holiday magic from @WaltDisneyWorld with @EmmaBunton and more of your favorite musical acts and Disney pals on The Wonderful World of Disney: Magical Holiday Celebration, Thanksgiving night on ABC.
It’s almost @NYRE time! Join hosts @RyanSeacrest, @lucyhale, @theebillyporter and @ciara for the festivities, December 31 at 8|7c on ABC. #RockinEve
ONE WEEK until @BradPaisley and friends take you on a wild ride through Nashville! Don't miss Brad Paisley Thinks He's Special Tuesday at 8|7c on ABC. #BradPaisleySpecial
